<h1>Postgraduate study&nbsp;</h1>
<p><img src="/media/computerscience/images/homepageimages/drone-banner.jpg" alt=""  title="" width="720" height="216"  /></p>
<p>Our range of specialist taught courses and research degrees are tailored to prepare you to meet the needs of industry. You will have access to expert supervision and world-class facilities, including dedicated postgraduate laboratories.</p>
<div class="col-half first-col"><p class="unpadded"><img src="/media/computerscience/images/homepageimages/pg-banner-1.jpg" alt=""  title="" width="350" height="109"  /></p>
<blockquote class="boxout">
<h2>On-campus Masters courses</h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.york.ac.uk/study/postgraduate-taught/courses/msc-advanced-computer-science/">MSc Advanced Computer Science</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.york.ac.uk/study/postgraduate-taught/courses/msc-artificial-intelligence/" title="MSc Artificial Intelligence">MSc Artificial Intelligence</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.york.ac.uk/study/postgraduate-taught/courses/msc-cyber-security/">MSc Cyber Security</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.york.ac.uk/study/postgraduate-taught/courses/msc-human-centred-interactive-technologies/">MSc Human-Centred Interactive Technologies</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.york.ac.uk/study/postgraduate-taught/courses/msc-safety-critical-systems-engineering/">MSc Safety Critical Systems Engineering</a></li>
<li><a title="Root &raquo; University Website &raquo; Sociology &raquo; Postgraduate study &raquo; Masters degrees &raquo; MSc in Social Media and Interactive Technologies" href="http://www.york.ac.uk/study/postgraduate/courses/msc-social-media-interactive-technology/">MSc Social Media and Interactive Technologies</a></li>
</ul>
<h3>Find out more:</h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.york.ac.uk/study/postgraduate-research/why-york/">Masters study: Why York?</a></li>
<li><a href="/postgraduate/accreditation/" title="Professional accreditation of our courses">Professional accreditation of our courses</a></li>
<li><a href="/postgraduate/postgraduate-preparing-to-study/" title="Preparing to study an MSc in Computer Science">Preparing to study an MSc in Computer Science</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.york.ac.uk/study/postgraduate-taught/why-york/careers-skills/">Enhance your career prospects</a></li>
</ul>
</blockquote>
<p class="unpadded"><img src="/media/computerscience/images/homepageimages/pg-banner-4.jpg" alt=""  title="" width="350" height="109"  /></p>
<blockquote class="boxout">
<h2>Online Masters courses</h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://online.york.ac.uk/study-online/msc-computer-science-online/">MSc Computer Science Online</a></li>
<li><a href="https://online.york.ac.uk/study-online/msc-computer-science-with-data-analytics-online/">MSc Computer Science with Data Analytics Online</a></li>
<li><a href="https://online.york.ac.uk/study-online/msc-computer-science-with-cyber-security-online/">MSc Computer Science with Cyber Security Online</a></li>
<li><a href="https://online.york.ac.uk/study-online/msc-computer-science-with-artificial-intelligence-online/">MSc Computer Science with Artificial Intelligence Online</a></li>
</ul>
<h3>Funding opportunities</h3>
<p><span>We have over 60 scholarships jointly funded by the Office for Students and ETAS to support students from non-computing backgrounds on our 100% online programmes. </span></p>
<p><span>To be eligible, applicants must h</span>ave an unconditional offer to study either the MSc Computer Science with Data Analytics online or MSc Computer Science with Artificial Intelligence online.</p>
<p><span>Successful applicants will receive a &pound;10,000 scholarship and a 10 per cent discount on their tuition fees. <a title="AI &amp; Data Science Scholarships" href="https://online.york.ac.uk/ofs-scholarships-tc/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Find out more about the Artificial Intelligence and Data Science Scholarships</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<h2>Funding for postgraduate taught courses</h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.york.ac.uk/study/postgraduate-taught/funding/" title="Funding options" target="_blank">Funding options to help with tuition fees and living costs</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.york.ac.uk/study/postgraduate-taught/funding/uk/loans/">UK government Masters loans</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.york.ac.uk/study/postgraduate-taught/funding/international/">Funding for international (including EU) students</a></li>
</ul>
<blockquote class="boxoutAlt">
<h2>Contact us</h2>
<p>If you'd like further information about our postgraduate courses, please get in touch with us:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>For on-campus taught Masters (MSc) courses</strong> -&nbsp;<a title="Email our Postgraduate Taught Admissions Team" href="mailto:cs-pgt-admissions@york.ac.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">cs-pgt-admissions@york.ac.uk</a></li>
<li><strong>For online taught Masters (MSc) courses </strong>-&nbsp;<a href="mailto:admissions@online.york.ac.uk">admissions@online.york.ac.uk</a>&nbsp;</li>
<li><strong>For PhD and Masters (by research) courses&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </strong>- <a title="Email PGR Admissions team" href="mailto:cs-pgr-admissions@york.ac.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">cs-pgr-admissions@york.ac.uk</a></li>
</ul>
</blockquote>
