<h2>Virtual tours</h2>
<p>Take a virtual tour of modern, dedicated facilities.</p>
<p><a href="https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=aPRYVvp8ra6"><img src="/media/computerscience/images/360scanthumbs/Computer-Science-foyer-pod-thumb-300.jpg" alt=""  title="" width="300" height="168"  /><br /></a><a href="https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=aPRYVvp8ra6">Department foyer and study pod tour</a>: our pod&nbsp;space is available 24/7 for individual and group study with kitchen facilities.</p>
<p><a href="https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=MR8A2XXkcYA"><img src="/media/computerscience/images/360scanthumbs/Computer-Science-Software-lab-thumb-300.jpg" alt=""  title="" width="300" height="169"  /><br /></a><a href="https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=MR8A2XXkcYA">Software lab tour</a>: we offer 24/7 access to our software labs for individual and group work.</p>
<p><a href="https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=vtq5SUEJJL4"><img src="/media/computerscience/images/360scanthumbs/Computer-Science-Hardware-lab-thumb-300.jpg" alt=""  title="" width="300" height="168"  /><br /></a><a href="https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=vtq5SUEJJL4">Hardware lab tour</a>: in the&nbsp;hardware lab you'll be introduced to the basics of computer architecture, operating systems and program language construction.</p>
